Jordan buys 50 , 000 tonnes U . S . wheat at $ 178 . 85 / T . Jordan on Thursday bought 50 , 000 tonnes of U . S . hard red winter or hard red spring wheat for second half October shipment at $ 178 . 85 per tonne , traders said . Jordan bought last Tuesday 50 , 000 tonnes of U . S . wheat for October shipment from Continental Grain at $ 178 . 80 per tonnes . It decided to delay purchase of another 50 , 000 tonnes to Thursday while bringing forward the shipment period to second half October from November . Traders said Jordan purchased the wheat from Dreyfus . - - Amman Newsroom + 9626623776 
